=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw 今日始終有至少廿幾個義士比狗拉咗，我地一定要檢討，唔可以再有手足比狗拉<br />\n<br />\n我認為有警察做臥底混入示威者，然後呼籲大家死守，之後防暴警察順理成章拉人，呢個可能性大啲，因為之前示威者入面有鬼已經有前科<br />\n<br />\n所以將來應該要定好一個策略，以撚狗為主，啲狗一上曬裝即將集體後退，要有隊形咁集體後退，會唔會咁樣好啲？<br />\n<br />\n始終見住有義士比人拉，我個心好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可唔可以一見到對家一武裝上嚟就即刻有隊形咁走，之前圍中環海濱軍營嗰日明明好齊心，大叫一二一二咁走，以後可唔可以咁？我唔想再有人拉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"714ec90f65316832313cecf5f7a502a79f73a34e","tid":1409942,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:20:22.000Z","msg":"lung cheung road still ok!"},{"pid":"ce6c66bfc6a685373b395d74aa5f0b2e4a1b3380","tid":1409942,"uid":106082,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:20:26.000Z","msg":"公司已經要人巴士返<br />\n大家幫手塞陸路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad46e069e6700857e23757dde0635d027ee047ba","tid":1409942,"uid":147454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:20:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"26e6523be2736a6d8fd25f0f1706ce430bf0c271","tid":1409942,"uid":56076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:21:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49ed5429ab942a9007300fc5085a0c1fc0d348c8","tid":1409942,"uid":56076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:22:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f269995e5449c7c12e317b3e7fe246f893841f3c","tid":14099