d":1409942,"uid":56076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:49:50.000Z","msg":"過陸路啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87ecaf6e843d91272c81da4f2662493cce6b60f0","tid":1409942,"uid":132454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:50:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9683bd92bd44054e87edd8deab4a184357cd3e7","tid":1409942,"uid":106958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:51:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"30116e2801986aa3a17c48337f6560dbbcf79030","tid":1409942,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:51:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">公路！公路！</span></span>"},{"pid":"7badf21bbc76f6bf0708d0ad249be88a64e514a9","tid":1409942,"uid":110403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:52:02.000Z","msg":"屯公求下咁多位車手塞死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6f26ef14a1a4867b34e454fe565fea1c65b9722","tid":1409942,"uid":99001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:52:24.000Z","msg":"如果俾人插可以咁對答<br />\n➡️阻住我返工<br />\n❌粗口<br />\n⭕️我都好想返工啊<br />\n➡️阻住我哋啲市民/冇人支持你㗎<br />\n❌阻乜x嘢啊<br />\n⭕️支持警察執法（成立獨立調查委員會）<br />\n➡️你咪去攪林鄭囉，攪我地啲小市民做嘜？<br />\n⭕️係林鄭搞緊小市民<br />\n⭕️係囉，佢唔出黎喎，要求政府回應！佢月薪40萬咖<br />\n⭕️唔好搞人屋企咁冇品，人地都有屋企人，屋企人係無辜咖！<br />\n⭕️林鄭好多屋企，唔知佢訓邊<br />\n⭕️林鄭成個政府都冇鬼用，淨係識搵警察出黎打人，自己就匿埋，搞到愈來愈多人出黎示威<br />\n(將責任推俾政府，強調示威者都係被逼)<br />\n➡️本人撐你都變到唔撐啦<br />\n⭕️請你體諒，宜家每星期都有好多流血衝突，好多年輕人受重傷，咁落去香港就黎打仗乜都冇，堵錢堵路已經係最和平嘅方法去施壓俾政府<br />\n⭕️其實我哋而家唔係要爭取同意,係希望政府可以回應依家社會發生緊嘅嘢<br />\n⭕️你唔需要撐我，撐警察就得，支持成立獨立調査委員會😂<br />\n➡️成班死癈青，淨係識攪事<br />\n⭕️今日好多律師會計師公務員都罷工呀，政府太過分，天怒人怨<br />\n⭕️如果政府真係有做嘢就唔會咁多死癈青啦，收納税人咁多錢又唔做嘢，一日到黑只係識得譴責！<br />\n➡️粗口<br />\n❌粗口回應<br />\n⭕️嘩支持政府嘅人咁暴力嘅😱<br />\n⭕️嘩！問候我哋呢啲小市民<br />\n⭕️你與其責備我地搞事不如責備下呢個暴力制度嘅政府<br />\n⭕️我明嘅，你係想鬧個政府搞到啲人出黎示威<br />\n⭕️我都好嬲呀，講左咁多次訴求，政府都漠示民意<br />\n⭕️車長！有人講粗口，違反香港鐵路附例呀！罰佢$5000！"},{"pid":"fe06ca32cf10209b9199e8635b30f2fed96a5497","tid":1409942,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:52:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"41e78a1c49f3c9a34294e11c386b8714840642e9","tid":1409942,"uid":139676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:52:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"372681c496628500357e2f394e2b4082183ce94a","tid":1409942,"uid":81702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:53:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ce6699d7117a26d2783e6e2a9df1d9e0377bdcbf","tid":1409942,"uid":56076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:54:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53a3378ec3695eb6c5b3818da4346234a32eb335","tid":1409942,"uid":56076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:54:38.000Z","msg":"陸路要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b51a023bca93ad97b2f9b6a6ecab050c3282d42","tid":1409942,"uid":61832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:55:00.000Z","msg":"欖隧啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82e36cfafd595654ff5ffce406f0f8195a2e11e7","tid":1409942,"uid":56076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:55:07.000Z","msg":"陸路要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8464869ed36452c83059204ee009fae27dc4eee1","tid":1409942,"uid":56076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:57:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c86e82518defbe7a2e314e8f7de2499cdea7c04","tid":1409942,"uid":96460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:57:35.000Z","msg":"東隧:好順<br />\n西隧: 塞(有位郁)<br />\n紅隧: 塞to the max<br />\n大圍迴旋: 有空位郁動，開始開車<br />\n彩虹迴旋處：正常"},{"pid":"c18fccbddd5359a5dce1f3ee325faaaa7a5d8b92","tid":1409942,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:58:07.000Z","msg":"巴士仲好暢順"},{"pid":"c22d90ad99600a2bea4463106a9ec47a715f0b5d","tid":1409942,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"841c742ff5efe71887dc3195f1c1e439baf0928d","tid":1409942,"uid":226955,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:20:08.000Z","msg":"喺堵塞交通呢件事上面，大家要避免陷入群眾鬥群眾嘅陷阱，可能之後開始會有（犬儒/ 廢老/ 五毛）會吹風話示威者今次真係擾到民，鬧示威者喺度搞三搞四，但係請大家諗深一層，係啲乜嘢原因令到班示威者要咁樣做？歸根究底係政府冇回應五大訴求呀，警察開槍射頭，虐打手無寸鐵示威者，放任埋黑社會周街打人放煙花，警察仲要同黑社會有講有笑呀，催淚彈放題、開槍打頭、唔比食藥，已經有好幾個義士暈低咗未醒返，又有少女比黑警除曬底褲將少女私處暴露喺眾人面前，大家如果要指責，請向政府指責，而唔係好似呢幅漫畫「某文化」咁，反而指責為人民向奴隸主抗爭嘅示威者。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/saa7Rku.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsaa7Rku.png&h=58898183&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日係勝仗，由旺角打到去尖沙咀再兜返去九龍城之後回馬槍去埋黃大仙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />紅隨仲塞咗兩次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw 今日始終有至少廿幾個義士比狗拉咗，我地一定要檢討，唔可以再有手足比狗拉<br />\n<br />\n我認為有警察做臥底混入示威者，然後呼籲大家死守，之後防暴警察順理成章拉人，呢個可能性大啲，因為之前示威者入面有鬼已經有前科<br />\n<br />\n所以將來應該要定好一個策略，以撚狗為主，啲狗一上曬裝即將集體後退，要有隊形咁集體後退，會唔會咁樣好啲？<br />\n<br />\n始終見住有義士比人拉，我個心好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可唔可以一見到對家一武裝上嚟就即刻有隊形咁走，之前圍中環海濱軍營嗰日明明好齊心，大叫一二一二咁走，以後可唔可以咁？我唔想再有人拉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:58:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bf952f44ca0fbf8d01d8e3fe23182d75a209df8f","tid":1409942,"uid":89882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:59:58.000Z","msg":"推 需要大量學神練車<br />\n需要大量死車"},{"pid":"71e495249b59f3e575e7b245810654dd7de08939","tid":1409942,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:00:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"252c7bba186f02fd6c71fc08b4bd4cf7c9684b0f","tid":1409942,"uid":56076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:00:46.000Z","msg":"東隧要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb2d5005f36dbcaa915ac0ff57a70f6924791660","tid":1409942,"uid":56076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:00:56.000Z","msg":"東隧要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59bbd4e9dd6427b31b259bf76b48e93f01c9a6ca","tid":1409942,"uid":56076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:01:15.000Z","msg":"東隧要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86796feef3e6c0572d6ab9e19918aa6eade55c76","tid":1409942,"uid":56076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:01:30.000Z","msg":"東隧要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb86813fd222f8450865363db7f8b069664305a4","tid":1409942,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:01:48.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style